author: Christina Zhao
title: Wuhan COVID-19 Death Toll May Be in Tens of Thousands, Data on Cremations and Shipments of Urns Suggest
description: Shipments of urns further raised questions about the accuracy of China's official Wuhan COVID-19 death toll.
